    title:
      "Challenges of deep learning methods for COVID-19 detection using public datasets",
    authors:
      "M K Hasan, M A Alam, L Dahal, S Roy, S R Wahid, M T E Elahi, R Martí, B Khanal",
    venue: "Informatics in Medicine Unlocked",
